cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about keyphrase generation, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves training and evaluating neural models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning).
